<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨晚下雪了！” 哈利说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以去滑雪橇吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去滑雪场吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米找出了围巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗穿上了雪地裤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈利系好了雪地靴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸把雪橇放进了车里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们走吧！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一家人开车去了滑雪场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>停车场在雪道下方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“滑雪橇会很有趣的。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！好高啊！” 奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈利抱怨说：“我们得走上去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太陡了！” 艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在手机上查好了地图。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪道上方也有停车场，” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把车停在那儿吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都回到车里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把车开到另一个停车场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里更好。” 哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米飞快地滑下去。“哇啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她撞到了一个雪堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咣！哈利撞到了艾米。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗撞到了什么，从雪橇上飞了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，爸爸、妈妈飞快地滑了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都躺在雪里大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爱滑雪橇。” 奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们再来一次吧！” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈利看着雪道，抱怨说：“啊！我们还得走上去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>